	* render/imagebuffer.cpp 1.117:
		- When adding micropolygons, include any micropolygons which overlap the
		  edges of the current bucket.  Previously, only micropolygons which were
		  completely within the current bucket were kept.

	* render/imagebuffer.cpp 1.118:
		Reverted my previous commit

2003-06-17  pgregory
	* Renderer.dsw 1.72:
		Inlcude the libslpp project.

	* Doxyfile 1.6:
