2003-06-04  pgregory
	* render/attributes.cpp 1.25:
	* render/nurbs.cpp 1.62:
	* render/patch.cpp 1.53:
	* render/quadrics.cpp 1.49:
	* render/ri.cpp 1.197:
	* render/subdivision2.cpp 1.24:
	* render/surface.cpp 1.43:
	* render/surface.h 1.45:
		Fix grid size calculation. No longer is dependent on the bucket
		size, but defaults to 256, and can be user set. Setting it on
		the bucket size makes not sense, the result of this was that at
		high shading rate settings we were getting lots of 1x1 grids.

