2003-05-31  pgregory
	* render/subdivision2.cpp 1.23:
		Fix u/v coordinates. When splitting to a patch, the patch gets
		the canonical u/v (0,0  1,0  0,1  1,1), and when dicing an SDS
		patch directly it gets the same. Not sure if this is the
		correct behaviour but at least it gives reasonable u/v
		coordinates.

