2003-05-27  pgregory
	* render/version.h 1.29:
		Update version [nightly]

	* filebuffer/filebuffer.cpp 1.14:
	* framebuffer_glut/framebuffer_glut.cpp 1.17:
	* framebuffer_glut_z/framebuffer_glut_z.cpp 1.11:
	* libdd/dd.cpp 1.13:
	* libddmsimple/ddmsimple.cpp 1.14:
	* libddmsimple/ddmsimple.h 1.10:
	* libddmsock/ddmsock.cpp 1.33:
	* libddmsock/ddmsock.h 1.11:
	* libddmsock/displaydriver.h 1.10:
	* render/iddmanager.h 1.12:
	* render/renderer.cpp 1.64:
	* render/renderer.h 1.40:
	* render/ri.cpp 1.190:
	* shadowmap/shadowmap.cpp 1.10:
		Change the way additional parameters are handled by the display
		system so that they are passed through to the device for
		processing. Meaning A) devices can respond to user parameters
		that are relevent to them, and B) user parameters can be
		arbitrarily added and handled by the device without the need to
		update the core.

