	* render/teapot.cpp 1.14:
	* render/teapot.h 1.6:
		Add an optional fasttrack dice function to the normal dicing implementation, so that surfaces that can fill in a lot of primitive variables efficiently in one go can do. Only implemented on quadrics at the moment.
		Update and tidy the timings output from statistics. Now clearer and more accurate. Also shows how much of the total time for a frame was captured so that if we are missing something in the timings we'll notice.

