	* render/converter.cpp 1.2:
	* render/texturemap.cpp 1.74:
	* shadowmap/Makefile.am 1.7:
	* teqser/Makefile.am 1.11:
		Revamp the autoconf/automake support.
		AC_DISABLE_STATIC - disable statics libraries as default, speeds up build times.
		Moved the DEBUG flags back to jsut the main Makefile
		Do proper checks for log4cpp,glut,libtiff and libargparse
		Clean up linking of log4cpp
		Clean up linking of libtiff
		Conditional compilation of plugin code only where needed
		Plugins anounce an error if plugin support is not built in.
		Use standard techniques for parsers/scanners

