	* libslparse/parser.yxx 1.1:
	* libslparse/scanner.l 1.1:
	* libslparse/scanner.lxx 1.1:
		Move parser.y and scanner.l to yxx/lxx so that flex/bison automake support
		will correctly use C++ insteaad of C.

	* libshadervm/shadervm.cpp 1.26:
		Aqsltell can call into the shadervm with no current rendering context so
		we much check that the return value of QGetRenderContextI is valid before
		trying to retrieve Logger.

