2003-02-18  pgregory
	* aqsl/Makefile.am 1.14:
	* aqsl/aqsl.bat 1.1:
		Replacement for aqsl.exe. Does the same thing, simpler, should
		work on Win9x

	* aqsl/aqsl_win.cpp 1.10:
		Removed, no longer relevant.

	* Renderer.dsw 1.50:
	* aqsl/aqsl.dsp 1.7:
		Removed the Windows only aqsl.exe, it was only put in because I
		mistakenly presumed Win98 didn't support pipes, however, as it
		turns out, not only does Win98 support pipes, but aqsl.exe
		doesn't work on Win98. aqsl.bat now does the same job.

