		enum added

2003-02-03  pgregory
	* render/ri.cpp 1.140:
	* render/surface.cpp 1.35:
		Fix order of processing for default primitive variables. Now
		processes defaults AFTER user specified, so only implements
		defaults for s/t if not explicitly specified by the user.

	* shaders/shadowspot.sl 1.4:
		Added 'falloff' option to shadowspot, falloff =
		
		0 - no falloff,
		1 - linear falloff (1/r),
		2 - square falloff (1/r^2)
		
		Default is which mimics the default for spotlights.

	* shaders/shadowpoint.sl 1.2:
		Added 'falloff' option to shadowpoint, falloff =
		
		0 - no falloff,
		1 - linear falloff (1/r),
		2 - square falloff (1/r^2)
		
		Default is which mimics the default for pointlights.

