2002-12-21  pgregory
	* render/patch.cpp 1.50:
	* render/patch.h 1.22:
	* render/ri.cpp 1.124:
	* render/subdivision2.cpp 1.7:
		Fix patch primitive to allow specification of the native basis
		during the call to convert. Allows new subdivision primitive to
		create b-spline patches without needing to play with attributes.

