		factors alone.

2002-10-08  pgregory
	* ribfiles/nurbs.rib 1.11:
		Changed to contain tests for clamping and cp weighting.

	* render/imagebuffer.cpp 1.69:
	* render/imagebuffer.h 1.22:
	* render/occlusion.cpp 1.1:
	* render/occlusion.h 1.1:
