2002-08-23  pgregory
	* render/nurbs.cpp 1.41:
		Fix trimming.

	* render/libaqsis.dsp 1.25:
		Add new forwarddiff.h file to the project.

	* ribfiles/real_env_test.rib 1.2:
		Remove eyesplits kludge.

	* render/quadrics.cpp 1.35:
		Fix bug on cone, wasn't using zmin/max to calculate bound.
		Fix bug in splits functions wasn't discarding intermediate split surfaces if splitting again due to eyesplits.
		Remove extraneous SetPrimitiveVariables calls during split, it is called during copy construct.

	* render/imagebuffer.cpp 1.64:
		Make eyesplits situations less of a memory problem by putting
		split surfaces at the top of the queue. This way the eyesplit
		is resolved sooner with less intermediate surface allocations.

