2002-07-29  pgregory
	* aqsis/aqsis.cpp 1.32:
	* render/imagebuffer.cpp 1.59:
		Implement support for progress customization, now --progress
		enables progress display ala prman, and --progressformat sets
		the string to use for the progress display.

