		functionality. Almost at a point now where we can use the VM
		without the core.

	* libshaderexecenv/texturemap.cpp 1.3:
	* libshaderexecenv/texturemap.h 1.2:
	* render/texturemap.cpp 1.35:
	* render/texturemap.h 1.21:
		Move texture handling back into the core where it belongs, 
		other modules can access it via the new interfaces. This
		decision is due to the nature of the texture cacheing mechanism
		which is/will be very core specific.

	* libaqsistypes/spline.cpp 1.1:
	* libaqsistypes/spline.h 1.1:
	* render/spline.cpp 1.5:
	* render/spline.h 1.7:
		Move basic spline functionality into the libaqsistypes utility
		library where other projects can use it.

	* render/ilightsource.h 1.1:
	* render/isurface.h 1.1:
	* render/itexturemap.h 1.1:
	* render/itransform.h 1.1:
		New interface structures for non invasive access to core
		functionality.

