	* plugins/jpg2tif/jpg2tif.dsp 1.5:
	* plugins/pcx2tif/pcx2tif.dsp 1.4:
	* plugins/ppm2tif/ppm2tif.dsp 1.5:
	* plugins/tga2tif/tga2tif.dsp 1.2:
	* render/libaqsis.dsp 1.12:
	* shadowmap/shadowmap.dsp 1.9:
	* slpp/slpp.dsp 1.4:
	* teqser/teqser.dsp 1.4:
		Switch to using the latest versions of thrid party tools and
		libraries. Will break existing build. See BUILD for
		instructions.

2002-04-04  pgregory
	* BUILD 1.7:
		Update Win32 build instructions to indicate the restrictions on
		Bison versions.

	* librib2/librib2.dsp 1.7:
	* libslparse/libslparse.dsp 1.5:
		Switch back to using the older style command options to bison, 
		we now require UnxUtils bison 1.28, anything newer is a problem.

2002-04-03  pgregory
	* prep_install.bat 1.17:
		Remove libslxargs from the binary release, currently relies on
		too many other libraries.

	* Makefile.am 1.32:
	* configure.in 1.41:
		Updated version number ready for release.

	* aqsis.iss 1.2:
	* libslparse/libslparse.dsp 1.4:
	* prep_install.bat 1.16:
	* render/version.h 1.12:
		Update versioning info ready for a release.

2002-04-02  pgregory
	* render/quadrics.cpp 1.17:
		Fix potential overflow in grid estimation routine, spotted by
		Michel Joron.

2002-03-31  pgregory
	* render/trimcurve.cpp 1.10:
		Fix bug in trim curve evaluation code. Was using an unsigned
		integer as an index, then checking for >=0 as a terminator.

	* render/quadrics.cpp 1.16:
		Small changes when tracking down quadrics bug, NYI.

2002-03-27  pgregory
	* render/quadrics.cpp 1.15:
		Fix normal calculation to only do matrix multiply if the surface really can generate it's own normals.
		Take into account Orientation when calculating normals.

	* ribfiles/quads_test.rib 1.4:
	* ribfiles/std_st_test.rib 1.4:
	* ribfiles/uv_test.rib 1.4:
		Small changes to make tests more appropriate for regression
		testing, switch to using Sides 1 to test for Normal
		calculatioin problems.

2002-03-26  pgregory
	* render/quadrics.cpp 1.14:
		Force circle function to use 4 arcs to avoid innacuracies in
		the bound calculation. Should look into further to find out if
		a more optimal solution exists.

2002-03-22  pgregory
	* aqsis/aqsis.cpp 1.27:
		Output time spent rendering along with progress. Courtesy of
		Michel Joron.

2002-03-21  pgregory
	* render/imagebuffer.cpp 1.48:
	* render/micropolygon.cpp 1.26:
	* render/micropolygon.h 1.13:
	* render/patch.cpp 1.13:
	* render/polygon.cpp 1.8:
	* render/quadrics.cpp 1.13:
	* render/stats.cpp 1.13:
	* render/stats.h 1.15:
		Enable surfaces to generate Ng if they are able. Handle
		degenerate MPGs gracefully. Output missed MPG statistics, may
		help in choosing optimum ShadingRate/PixelSamples settings.

2002-03-19  pgregory
	* render/quadrics.cpp 1.11:
	* render/quadrics.h 1.7:
		Use proper quadrics with an approximating bound method based on
		NURBS hulls.

	* render/quadrics.cpp 1.12:
	* render/quadrics.h 1.8:
		Allow quadrics to specify their own normals.

