	* framebuffer_glut/framebuffer_glut.cpp 1.3:
	* libdd/dd.cpp 1.5:
	* libddmsock/ddmsock.cpp 1.3:
		* Fixed problem with aqsis_framebuffer_glut not letting-go of sockets (which prevented more than one from running at a time)
		* Fixed problem with idle function in aqsis_framebuffer_glut wasting CPU cycles

	* Makefile.am 1.14:
	* aqsis/Makefile.am 1.9:
	* configure.in 1.15:
	* framebuffer_glut/.cvsignore 1.1:
	* framebuffer_glut/Makefile.am 1.1:
	* framebuffer_glut/framebuffer_glut.cpp 1.1:
	* libddmsock/ddmsock.cpp 1.2:
		 Created framebuffer_glut, a libddmsocket-based device driver
		that uses the GLUT library for portable graphics / windowing.

