	* render/cellnoise.cpp 1.5:
		Yes Pinky.  Fincally really fixed the annoying cellnoise thing
		that has been bothering me.  It was a bug in the permute code
		that messed-up the swapping.  The tables are back to normal
		functioning and hopefully need no more changes.

