		causing compile errors on undefined version.h stuff.  This was
		on MS dsw project build.

	* render/ri.cpp 1.24:
		Changed sinc again to have a half cosine window and made it
		more radially symmetric.

	* render/ri.cpp 1.23:
		Fixed a possible divide by zero in the window sinc function.

