	* render/shadervm.h 1.4:
	* render/sstring.cpp 1.3:
	* render/subdivision.cpp 1.5:
	* render/subdivision.h 1.3:
	* render/texturemap.cpp 1.4:
	* render/texturemap.h 1.4:
		Use vector iterators where appropriate.
		Change WIN32 #ifdefs to AQSIS_SYSTEM_WIN32.
		Adopt appropriate changes from Linux port into Win32 version.

	* render/makefile.mingw 1.2:
		Bring up to date with latest win32 build.

	* render/aqsis_types.h 1.2:
	* render/subdivision.cpp 1.4:
		Remove dependency on logb, caused portability issues.
		Add fast pow2 code to standard header.

	* BUILD 1.2:
		Expand on the build process for libraries.

	* BUILD 1.3:
		Missed a TIFF export.

