2001-05-01  pgregory
	* render/surface.cpp 1.4:
		Fix the copy constructor to actually do a copy.

	* render/quadrics.h 1.3:
		Remove duplicated m_?DiceSize member variables, they are on
		CqBasicSurface where they are needed.

	* render/quadrics.cpp 1.3:
		Fix typo in the sphere dicing code.

	* render/polygon.cpp 1.4:
	* render/polygon.h 1.4:
		Add motion blurred points polygons.

	* render/patch.cpp 1.4:
		Fix bug in assignment operator, motion blur now works with
		patchmeshes.

	* render/renderer.cpp 1.4:
		Remove some crud.

	* render/micropolygon.cpp 1.4:
		Remove asserts in normal calculation code, should look into why
		they were asserting.

	* render/ri.cpp 1.4:
		Implement motion blurred points polygons.

